data.description: RELOCATION SPECIAL:  Two recent appraisals were completed and home was appraised at $625,000 on one appraisal and $620,000 on the other appraisal.   Wonderful offering in one of Hanover's most sought-after communities.  This home boasts a grand kitchen with countertop cooking, beautiful cabinetry, and spacious granite countertop and island - perfect for the most avid baker or chef.  The main level also features the formal living room, dining room, private office AND a large great room with access to the screened porch and entertaining deck.  The second level of this home holds 5 bedrooms - with a prominent primary bedroom, complete with walk-in closets, step-in glass and tile shower, double vanity, and dressing table.  The third level offers a spacious recreation room with full bath - perfect for overnight guests or social gatherings.  This home is situated on a park-like, cul-de-sac  homesite.  The Milestone neighborhood offers: tennis and basketball courts, swimming pool, playground, clubhouse and gym.
